article_id:2704,category_name:News,title_name:Year-End Event Information,image_path:,message:<div>Year-end events start on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640325600"></span>!</div><div><br></div><hr><div>1. A Daily Free Tenfold Summon Event Is Coming!</div><div><br></div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which allows you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, is coming!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640930400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1641362399"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/news/detail/2666">See here for further information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>2. The New Year&#39;s Special Bonus Is Coming!</div><div><br></div><div>The New Year&#39;s Special Bonus starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1641016800"></span>. Log in during the bonus to get gifts until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1642053599"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1641016800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1642053599"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/news/detail/2703">See here for further information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>3. Lucky Letters Are Coming!</div><div><br></div><div>You can collect lucky letters during the distribution period from log-in bonuses and limited-time endeavors. When you log in during the raffle period in the new year, a prize from first to seventh prize will be randomly selected for each lucky letter you collected, and you will receive an item based on the prize tier.</div><div><br></div><div>■Distribution Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640325600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1641016799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Raffle Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1641016800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1642139999"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/news/detail/30003">See here for further information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>4. New Year&#39;s Party Packs Are Coming!</div><div><br></div><div>New Year&#39;s Party Packs will be available for purchase in the Shop starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640930400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability Period</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640930400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1642053599"></span></div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/news/detail/2706">See here for further information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>5. Upgrade Events Are Coming!</div><div><br></div><div>Various events, including half stamina for Advanced Dragon Trials and The Agito Uprising and daily triple drops for certain quests, start on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640584800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en-gb/news/detail/10079">See here for further information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>6. The Celestial Showdown Raid Event Is Coming!</div><div><br></div><div>The Celestial Showdown raid event starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640930400"></span>. Challenge the raid boss in event-exclusive quests and earn some great rewards!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1640930400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1642053599"></span></div><div><br></div><hr><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1640325600,update_time1640327584